div.div:
In this diagram, we illustrate instance level representation for the process
that a specific student, Mary, receives two different awards. One is the
award for Kentucky Hackathon, which is an award that funded by Restricted
Gift. The amount is over 500$ thus it will be approved by the Provost. Another
award is from CS Department for the winner in 2019 winter football game. It is
an award funded by Unrestricted General Funds, which means it will be approved
by the Dean.
The awd namespace represents the Student Award schema and I've used the
default namespace for instance resources.
